{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"20425d4d-8b9b-4a7f-8a0b-bf6030ed3129","content":"I can help guide you through analyzing your crash dump. The `dump-collect` skill I have available is specifically for **collecting** dumps, not analyzing them — so let me help you directly.\n\nHere are the main tools for .NET crash dump analysis:\n\n### `dotnet-dump analyze`\n```bash\ndotnet tool install -g dotnet-dump\ndotnet-dump analyze your-file.dmp\n```\nUseful commands inside the analyzer:\n- `clrstack` — managed call stack of the crashing thread\n- `pe` (print exception) — show the last exception\n- `dumpheap -stat` — heap summary (for OOM crashes)\n- `threads` — list all threads\n- `setthread <id>` + `clrstack` — inspect other threads\n\n### LLDB (Linux)\n```bash\ndotnet-sos install\nlldb --core your-file.dmp\n```\nThen use SOS commands like `clrstack`, `pe`, `dso`.\n\n### Visual Studio (Windows)\nOpen the `.dmp` file directly — it provides a rich UI for mixed-mode debugging.\n\n---\n\n**Quick triage steps:**\n1. Run `dotnet-dump analyze your.dmp`\n2. Run `pe` to check for an unhandled exception\n3. Run `clrstack` to see what code was executing\n4. If it's an OOM, run `dumpheap -stat` to find memory hogs\n\nWould you like me to install `dotnet-dump` and start analyzing the file? If so, let me know the path to your `.dmp` file.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f7c42fe6-23d7-4332-8c2f-ccb9ed15138a","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about analyzing a .dmp crash dump file. Let me check the available skills - there's a `dump-collect` skill, but its description specifically says:\n\n- USE FOR: enabling automatic crash dumps, capturing dumps, setting up dump collection\n- DO NOT USE FOR: analyzing or debugging dumps, post-mortem investigation with lldb/windbg/dotnet-dump analyze\n\nSo the dump-collect skill is NOT appropriate here. The user wants to *analyze* a dump, not collect one.\n\nLet me provide guidance on analyzing crash dumps myself.","outputTokens":506,"requestId":"2C41:1986A2:14AEDE6:1785B6C:69F94F27"},"id":"95b713ba-0af6-4a58-a5a1-3beb058cc65e","timestamp":"2026-05-05T02:00:22.215Z","parentId":"a1cd2aed-bfaf-4b5c-a4d6-ff8adfa77364"}
